<h2 id="abstract">Abstract</h2>

<p>This is a well known issue when the libssl got updated and most of the Linux distributions did update with it
Multiple solutions came across different blockchains, since we are based on bitcoin and blakecoin we might as well do some of this updates</p>

<h2 id="mip-workflow">MIP Workflow</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Research</li>
  <li>Setup test enviorment</li>
  <li>Fix</li>
  <li>Build and Test</li>
  <li>Release</li>
</ol>

